{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Clipboard.writeText()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/writeText","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Clipboard_API\">Clipboard API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Clipboard\"><code>Clipboard</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/read\"><code>read()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/readText\"><code>readText()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/write\"><code>write()</code></a></li><li><em><code>writeText()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Clipboard API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ClipboardEvent\"><code>ClipboardEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ClipboardItem\"><code>ClipboardItem</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator/clipboard\"><code>Navigator.clipboard</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Clipboard\"><code>Clipboard</code></a> 接口的&nbsp;<strong><code>writeText()</code></strong>&nbsp;方法可以写入特定字符串到操作系统的剪切板。</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> 规范要求在写入剪贴板之前使用 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Permissions_API\">Permissions API</a> 获取“剪贴板写入”权限。但是，不同浏览器的具体要求不同，因为这是一个新的 API。有关详细信息，请查看<a href=\"#浏览器兼容性\">浏览器兼容性</a> and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Clipboard#clipboard_availability\">Clipboard availability</a> in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Clipboard\">Clipboard</a>。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>promise</em> = navigator.clipboard.writeText(<em>newClipText</em>)</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"newcliptext\"><code>newClipText</code></dt>\n <dd>The <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> to be written to the clipboard.</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect3\">\n <h3 id=\"返回值\">返回值</h3>\n </dt>\n</dl>\n\n<p>一个<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> ，一旦剪贴板的内容被更新，它就会被解析。如果调用者没有写入剪贴板的权限，则拒绝写入剪切板（reject）</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<p>此示例将剪贴板的内容设置为字符串“&lt;empty clipboard&gt;”。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>clipboard<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">writeText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;empty clipboard&gt;\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/* clipboard successfully set */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/* clipboard write failed */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/clipboard-apis/#dom-clipboard-writetext","title":"Clipboard API and events"}],"query":"api.Clipboard.writeText"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.Clipboard.writeText","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/writeText/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"例子","id":"例子"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"Clipboard 接口的 writeText() 方法可以写入特定字符串到操作系统的剪切板。","popularity":0.0007,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Clipboard.writeText()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Clipboard.writeText()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/clipboard/writetext","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/clipboard/writetext/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Clipboard","title":"Clipboard"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/writeText","title":"Clipboard.writeText()"}],"pageTitle":"Clipboard.writeText() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}